what:	Spot o' Conf
where:  https://chiselapp.com/user/stwo/repository/spotoconf
who:	Stuart Cassoff <stwo@users.sourceforge.net>
why:	Tcl/Jim extension architecture.


Spot o' Conf is a TEA-inspired configure and build system
for Tcl and Jim extensions.

Features:
  *  Build binary or script-only extensions for Tcl or Jim.
  *  Build build/install documentation and examples.
  *  Run tests and make distribution files.
  *  Supports pkg-config.
  *  Extensible.
  *  Simple and fast.  
